    "19": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "# Database Dashboard\n\nThis dashboard Redis Enterprise Database level metrics. In Redis Enterprise a Database is the fundamental deployment unit, it may contain one or many underlying shards. The Database metrics are metrics that are rolled up for all of the underpinning shards in the Redis Database. Database metrics are prefixed with `endpoint` when they come in from prometheus."
    },
